name: YWPD-TC-333 - Verify that the user is able to Copy SWM Policy with web small dataset
description: The objective of this test case is to ensure that the users can successfully Copy SWM Policy with web small dataset

steps.name: Given The user successfully opened the yieldWerx web application and login
When Click on "SWM" in the left menu bar and click on SWM Policies
When See the list of already created SWM policies
When Click Copy button available infront of each already created policy
When Create SWM Policy Window will open
When Change name and description from in the General tab
When Make required changes in tabs
Then Verify that the copied policy has been saved and appears in the SWM Policies window

fullName: SWM Policies: YWPD-TC-333 - Verify that the user is able to Copy SWM Policy with web small dataset
